divs: sighting detailsi was on my front porch. i looked to the southeast, and noticed a light in the sky. i thought it was an airplane. i watched for the blinking lights, but there was none. it was a glowing light that was reddish\yellow\orange. it traveled in a straight line to the east. it made no observable noise. it disappeared to the west of my location. total duration - about 20 seconds.
Summary: Glowing light travelling from SE to W, then disappeared
